        <p>Twenty-one assets scored across five categories. The AI/data infrastructure thesis is the long-term conviction play — FET, TAO, RNDR, AGIX are the picks-and-shovels of the AI economy. But conviction doesn't override timing. <em>The model scores what the data says, not what the thesis wants.</em> Starting with a single BUY signal and building from there.</p>
